QuestData.Title: Is This Stuff Still Good?
QuestData.Description: You find what appears to be a crate of food, left behind when this camp was abandoned. On the outside of the crate, you can make out a stamp that says "PROPERTY OF MARSHAL EXPEDITIONS".$b$bPerhaps you might find someone who could use this?
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Crate of Foodstuffs to Williden Marshal at Marshal's Stand.
QuestData.RewardText: Oh... wow... it's some really old food. Hey Hol'anyee, take a look at this! This $r brought us those old rations that we abandoned!$b$bNo, not from Marshal's Refuge... from the old base camp!$b$b<Williden turns back toward you.>$b$bI'm not sure I want to peek inside. I'll just give it to Nolen, I guess... he'll know what to do with it.
